      "id": "60081657782c4b002220e257",
      "text": "ゲームループ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1611142758,
      "updated": 1611142758
    },
    {
      "id": "6008166c79d3a900007d3ab1",
      "text": "code:疑似コード",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1611142761,
      "updated": 1611142762
    },
    {
      "id": "6008166f79d3a900007d3ab3",
      "text": " while(true){",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1611142762,
      "updated": 1611142771
    },
    {
      "id": "6008167779d3a900007d3ab4",
      "text": "   ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1611142771,
      "updated": 1611142786
    },
    {
      "id": "6008168779d3a900007d3ab9",
      "text": "   // この中で状態を変化させたり条件分岐を列挙したりすることでゲームを実現する.",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1611142786,
      "updated": 1611142833
    },
    {
      "id": "6008169979d3a900007d3abb",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1611142806,
      "updated": 1611142815
    },
    {
      "id": "6008167879d3a900007d3ab6",
      "text": "   sleep 0.05sec",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1611142773,
      "updated": 1611142781
    },
    {
      "id": "6008167779d3a900007d3ab5",
      "text": " }",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1611142771,
      "updated": 1611142771
    },
    {
      "id": "6008166c79d3a900007d3ab2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1611142761,
      "updated": 1611142761
    },
    {
      "id": "600816c079d3a900007d3abd",
      "text": " [HSP]でバリバリ使ってた覚えがある",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1611142844,
      "updated": 1611142850
    },
    {
      "id": "600816c979d3a900007d3abf",
      "text": " \tイベントドリブン？コールバック？なにそれ美味しいの？",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1611142853,
      "updated": 1611142861
    },
    {
      "id": "6008171c79d3a900007d3ac4",
      "text": " \tsleepが0.1秒くらいだとキー入力が検知されない、0.01秒なら余裕だがCPU重たい、0.05秒くらいなら……",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1611142936,
      "updated": 1667001213
    },
    {
      "id": "6008173179d3a900007d3ac5",
      "text": " \t こういうバランス調整とかしていた",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1611142957,
      "updated": 1611142961
    },
    {
      "id": "6008176079d3a900007d3ac6",
      "text": " \t （HSPでは stick という命令で「その瞬間に指定キーが押されたかどうか判定する」という形でキー入力を検知する）",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1611143004,
      "updated": 1611143038
    },
    {
      "id": "600816c079d3a900007d3abe",
      "text": " [PySimpleGUI]も[Pyxel]もそうだなぁ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1611142844,
      "updated": 1611403472
    },
    {
      "id": "635c6c716eb4060000861d25",
      "text": " Arduinoのloopもこんな感じ",
